title: Andrew Cooper
text:
Banff, Calgary



Welcome to my personal website! I am currently a 5th year PhD candidate studying Statistics at Virginia Polytechnic and State University. Before that I received my Bachelors (’18) and Masters (’20) degrees in Statistics from Duke University.
